rows.label: qst710101_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, this is no good. It's gonna
take ages at this rate...

rows.label: qst710101_msg0002
rows.name:
Huh, you want me? You can ask
me anything you want... as
long as it's about insects!

rows.label: qst710101_msg0003
rows.name: What? You're not interested in insects?

rows.label: qst710101_msg0004
rows.name:
Tut, tut! Well, I tell you there's
more to insects than meets the eye!

rows.label: qst710101_msg0005
rows.name:
Their shiny shells, their
strong bendy legs...

rows.label: qst710101_msg0006
rows.name:
Plus if you boil them up, you get
some really useful medicines!

rows.label: qst710101_msg0008
rows.name:
I've collected loads of insects,
but 'cos I'm just a kid, I'm not
allowed to go looking very far.

rows.label: qst710101_msg0009
rows.name:
But I need to get lots of
insects as quickly as possible!

rows.label: qst710101_msg0010
rows.name:
D'you think you could bring
me any insects you find?

rows.label: qst710101_msg0011
rows.name:
Thanks! Oh, and I'll need some from
Gula too, not just from Iira!
